{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-203-squarefree-binomial-coefficients","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 203: Binomijalni koeficijenti bez kvadrata","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Binomijalni koeficijenti $\\displaystyle\\binom{n}{k}$ mogu se rasporediti u trougaonični oblik, trokutak Pascala, kao što sledi:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{array}{ccccccccccccccc}\n&#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;    &#x26;    &#x26;    &#x26;  1 &#x26;    &#x26;    &#x26;    &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   \\\\\n&#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;    &#x26;    &#x26;  1 &#x26;    &#x26; 1  &#x26;    &#x26;    &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   \\\\\n&#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;    &#x26;  1 &#x26;    &#x26;  2 &#x26;    &#x26;  1 &#x26;    &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   \\\\\n&#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;  1 &#x26;    &#x26;  3 &#x26;    &#x26;  3 &#x26;    &#x26;  1 &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   \\\\\n&#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26; 1 &#x26;    &#x26;  4 &#x26;    &#x26;  6 &#x26;    &#x26;  4 &#x26;    &#x26; 1 &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   \\\\\n&#x26;   &#x26; 1 &#x26;   &#x26;  5 &#x26;    &#x26; 10 &#x26;    &#x26; 10 &#x26;    &#x26;  5 &#x26;   &#x26; 1 &#x26;   &#x26;   \\\\\n&#x26; 1 &#x26;   &#x26; 6 &#x26;    &#x26; 15 &#x26;    &#x26; 20 &#x26;    &#x26; 15 &#x26;    &#x26; 6 &#x26;   &#x26; 1 &#x26;   \\\\\n1 &#x26;   &#x26; 7 &#x26;   &#x26; 21 &#x26;    &#x26; 35 &#x26;    &#x26; 35 &#x26;    &#x26; 21 &#x26;   &#x26; 7 &#x26;   &#x26; 1 \\\\\n&#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;   &#x26;    &#x26;    &#x26;    &#x26; \\ldots\n\\end{array}$$</p>\n<p>Izgleda da prvih osam redova Pascalovog trougla imaju dvanaest različitih brojeva: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 10, 15, 20, 21 i 35.</p>\n<p>Pozitivan ceo broj n naziva se kvadratno slobodan ako ga nijedan kvadrat prostog broja ne deli. Od dvanaest različitih brojeva u prvih osam redova Pascálovog trougla, svi osim 4 i 20 su kvadratno slobodni. Ukupan broj različitih kvadratno slobodnih brojeva u prvih osam redova je 105.</p>\n<p>Pronađite zbir različitih brojeva bez kvadrata u prvih 51 redova Pascalovog trougla.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4381000cf542c50ff4a","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301844,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-203-squarefree-binomial-coefficients"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function squarefreeBinomialCoefficients() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nsquarefreeBinomialCoefficients();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>squarefreeBinomialCoefficients()</code> treba da vrati <code>34029210557338</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(squarefreeBinomialCoefficients(), 34029210557338);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-203-squarefree-binomial-coefficients","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-204-generalised-hamming-numbers","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-202-laserbeam","id":"5900f4381000cf542c50ff4a","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles"